content.rendered:
Facetasm Spring Summer 2024 during Paris Fashion Week.

Coming of Age.


This is a fantasy collection created from the memories and feelings of a landscape..

" We would like to take this opportunity express our gratitude to all our partners and collaborators. Thank you from the bottom of our hearts.

And thank you to the people who have always helped us, everyone at the factories, pattern makers, staff, family and friends.

We would like to express our gratitude to everyone who always supports FACETASM with great love. We are pleased to present our collection."

- Hiromichi Ochiai

Runway looks

Text and Photo: Press Facetasm.

More on: @facetasmtokyo

Thanks: @radical.pr


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
